 "cells": [

   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Machine à laver le linge\n",
    "\n",
    "Le fichier {download}`data/machine_a_laver.wav` contient le bruit d'une machine à laver le linge lors de l'essorage. Quelle est la fréquence de rotation du tambour ? "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "501f2f54",
   "metadata": {
    "tags": [
     "sol"
    ]
   },
   "source": [
    "--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n",
    "\n",
    "## Solution"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "id": "75d2d9ad",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from scipy.io.wavfile import read\n",
    "from numpy.fft import rfft, rfftfreq\n",
    "from matplotlib.pyplot import figure\n",
    "import numpy as np"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "id": "0282d641",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "samplerate, amplitude = read('data/machine_a_laver.wav')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "id": "396e39d6",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "44100\n",
      "414380\n",
      "9.396371882086168\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "print(samplerate)\n",
    "delta_t = 1/samplerate\n",
    "N = len(amplitude)\n",
    "print(N)\n",
    "T = N*delta_t\n",
    "print(T)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "id": "456bf33f",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "amplitude_tilde = rfft(amplitude)\n",
    "freq = rfftfreq(N, delta_t)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "id": "fd722ed6",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 432x288 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "fig = figure()\n",
    "ax = fig.subplots(1, 1)\n",
    "\n",
    "ax.loglog(freq, np.abs(amplitude_tilde)**2)\n",
    "ax.set_ylim(1E-3, None)\n",
    "\n",
    "ax.set_xlabel('Frequence [Hz]')\n",
    "ax.set_ylabel('Puissance [u.a]')\n",
    "\n",
    "ax.grid(which='both')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "b3221149",
   "metadata": {
    "tags": [
     "sol"
    ]
   },
   "source": [
    "La fréquence typique de rotation est de 1200 tours par minutes, soit environ 20 Hz. Il s'agir du pic de gauche. On zoom dessus."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 11,
   "id": "ea109613",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "Text(0, 0.5, 'Puissance [u.a]')"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 11,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 432x288 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "mask = np.abs(freq-20)<5\n",
    "\n",
    "fig = figure()\n",
    "ax = fig.subplots(1, 1)\n",
    "\n",
    "ax.semilogy(freq[mask], np.abs(amplitude_tilde[mask])**2)\n",
    "ax.grid()\n",
    "\n",
    "i = np.argmax(np.abs(amplitude_tilde[mask])**2)\n",
    "freq_max = freq[mask][i]\n",
    "amp_max = np.abs(amplitude_tilde[mask][i])**2\n",
    "\n",
    "ax.semilogy(freq_max, amp_max, 'ko')\n",
    "ax.text(freq_max, amp_max, f'  {freq_max:.2f} Hz')\n",
    "\n",
    "ax.set_xlabel('Frequence [Hz]')\n",
    "ax.set_ylabel('Puissance [u.a]')"
   ]
  }
 ],
